Georges Rouquier https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Georges_Rouquier 0 Georges Rouquier (23 June 1909 – 19 December 1989) was a French actor, film director and screenwriter. He appeared in 8 films between 1942 and 1982. He also directed twenty five films between 1942 and 1983.
